title.en: Shingeki no Kyojin - Guide to Raising an Eren (Doujinshi)

description.en:
Very short practical guide on how to raise a healthy child. If you ever wondered about the following*:

- How do i feed an infant?
- What games do they enjoy?
- Can i keep mine in cage?
- Do they have to be cleaned in a tub, or will five minutes in washing machine suffice?

This book is definitely for you! It contains the answers to ten most crucial issues concerning proper parenting.

*On an unrelated note, please consult your physician about permanent contraception methods. Knowing is half the battle, and in this case sterilisation makes the other.
